quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  12,96,"Nde humpitoowo Yaaquuba on ko welata mo arunoo, o werlii dolokke Yuusufa on ka yeeso makko, o wonti yi'oowo. O maakani ﾉ妬ﾉ遼兎 makko ﾉ兎n: E mi yeetanooki on miﾉ熔 anndi e neweende Alla nden e moﾆｴﾆｴere Makko nden ko on anndaa onon?"
  12,97,"ﾆ（ﾉ遼兎 makko ﾉ兎n ngatinanii ben maﾉ橡兎 Yaaquuba (yo o his) ko ﾉ兎 waﾉ擁 kon Yuusufa e miﾃｱan-mun, ﾉ兎 wi'i: Ko an yo ben amen, ﾉ預ﾉ橡妬ran-men ka Alla haforaneede junuubi amen yawtuﾉ擁 ﾉ擁n. Menen men laatinoke junubante bonnuﾉ兎 e ko men waﾉ擁 kon Yuusufa e neene-gooto makko on."
  12,98,"Ben maﾉ橡兎 maakani ﾉ兎: Aray ka mi ﾉ預ﾉ橡妬rana on Joomi am haforannede. Ko Kanko woni Haforoowo junuubi tuubooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n e jeyaaﾉ兎 Makko ﾉ兎n, Hinnotooﾉ熔 ﾉ兎."
  12,99,"Annabi Yaaquuba yaltidi e ﾉ兎ynguure makko nden ka leydi maﾉ橡兎, ﾉ兎 sutii ka Yuusufu Misra. Nde ﾉ兎 naatunoo ka makko, o ﾉ殿ttiniti mawﾉ兎 makko ﾉ兎n ﾉ擁ﾉ熔 e makko, o maakani musiﾉ遼兎 makko ﾉ兎n e ﾉ兎ynguure maﾉ橡兎 nden: Naatiree Misra muuyﾉ容 Alla, ko on hooliiﾉ兎, bone woo memataa on."
  12,100,"O toolni mawﾉ兎 makko ﾉ兎n ﾉ擁ﾉ熔 ka danki makko, ontuma ﾉ兎 hiwrori mo kamﾉ兎 e musiﾉ遼兎 makko ﾉ兎n sappo e go'o sujjugol. Ngol sujjugol wanaa dewal, ko teddungal, yahdungol e yamiroore Alla nden wano ardiri non ka koyﾉ熔l. Ko ﾉ蓉m waﾉ擁 si Yuusufa maakani ben makko: Ngol hiwrorgol lam ﾉ熔o sujjugol, ko firo koyﾉ熔l am ngol oya tuma ngol mi fillaninoo on. Gomﾉ擁i Joomi am waﾉ擁i ngol goonga, O moﾆｴﾆｴike kadi e am tuma O yaltinnoo lam ka kaso O itti on onon kadi ka ladde, ﾉ殿awo nde seytaane bonni hakkunde am e musiﾉ遼兎 am ﾉ兎n. Pellet, Joomi am ko newaniiﾉ熔 toppitagol ko O muuyi kon. Pellet, ko Kanko woni Annduﾉ熔 fiyakuuji jeyaaﾉ兎 Makko ﾉ兎n, ﾃ粗eﾃｱuﾉ熔 e toppitagol Makko ngol."
  12,101,"Refti yuusufa torii Joomi makko, o maaki: Joomi am, gomﾉ擁i A yeﾉ擁i lam laamagol Misra, A anndinii lam kadi firo koyﾉ擁. An Tagirﾉ熔 kammuuli ﾉ擁n e leydi ndin e noone mo aldah e yeru gadano, Ko An woni giﾉ熔 heftuﾉ熔 denndaangal fiyakuuji am ﾉ擁n aduna e laakara. ﾆｳettitam tuma lajal am timmata ko mi juulﾉ熔, waﾉ葉idaa lam e Annabaaﾉ兎 moﾆｴﾆｴuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, immorde e baabiraaﾉ兎 am ﾉ兎n e woﾉ遼兎 goo, ka Aljanna firdawsi toowuﾉ熔."
  12,102,"Ko jantaa koo e qissa Yuusufa e musiﾉ遼兎 makko ﾉ兎n, Meﾉ容n wahayina ﾉ蓉m e maaﾉ預, an Nulaaﾉ熔. A anndaano ﾉ蓉m, tawde a tawanooka ka musiﾉ遼兎 Yuusufa ﾉ兎n eﾉ橡砥noo werlagol mo ka niwre woyndu, ﾉ兎 fewji pewje maﾉ橡兎. Men anndire ﾉ蓉m wahyu on."
  12,103,"Ko ﾉ砥ri ﾉ蓉uﾉ蓉de e yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, hay si a etike, an Nulaaﾉ熔, ﾉ兎 gomﾉ擁ntaa. Wata a naﾉ妬r wonkii maa kin e maﾉ橡兎 ninse."